kabasuji.model

Class PuzzleLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • kabasuji.model.Level
      • kabasuji.model.PuzzleLevel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class PuzzleLevel
extends Level
    This class extends Level class to get the shared logic between the different types of levels. It contains the specific puzzle level logic for example the number of moves information.
    Author:
    Ethan
